====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|chess}} The most common [[chess]] piece, or a similar piece in a similar game. In chess each side has eight; moves are only [[forward]], and [[attack]]s are only forward diagonally or [[en passant]].
# {{lb|en|figurative}} Someone who is being [[manipulate]]d or [[use]]d to some end.
#: {{ux|en|Though a '''pawn''' of the gods, her departure is the precipitating cause of the Trojan War.}}

